title: Should I Join Tik Tok?
description:
I've been hearing that it would be good for my channel if I put up clips on tik tok...I really don't want to get sucked into another social media platform but I'm being told its a smart move to get my content out there...I'm conflicted and need your help!

Follow me on twitter @AndreaLynnLewis
Follow me on Insta: @vintage_bangs
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
